## Integration Flow (as implemented in `main.py`)

```
main()
│
├─ 1. run_login_menu()          ← hospital_login logic (cleaned, FIX-04)
│       └─ _login_user()        ← SHA-256 hashed, SQLite-backed
│
├─ 2. database.init_db()        ← creates hospital.db table
│
├─ 3. Thread: PatientMonitor    ← patient_monitor.generate_patient_data()
│       └─ prints every 10 s
│
├─ 4. Thread: Ambulance         ← publishes JSON to test.mosquitto.org (FIX-02)
│       └─ every 10 s
│
└─ 5. Main thread: Hospital     ← subscribes to test.mosquitto.org (FIX-02)
        ├─ display_patient_update()
        ├─ _map_keys_for_db()   ← key translation layer (FIX-03)
        └─ database.save_data() ← correct function name (FIX-01)
```

